<section id="typography" data-brand-section class="melis-section">
  <div class="melis-section-eyebrow-row">
    <span class="num">07</span>
    <span class="name">Type · three families</span>
    <span class="line"></span>
  </div>
  <h2 class="melis-section-title">Three typefaces. No fourth. Each has a job.</h2>

  <div class="melis-prose">
    <p>A modern Garamond for display. A neutral grotesque for everything else. A monospace for structural metadata. The three are deliberately differentiated — never blur the lines between them.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="type-specimens">
    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div class="type-meta">
        <span>Family<strong>Cormorant Garamond</strong></span>
        <span>Role<strong>Display</strong></span>
        <span>Weights<strong>300 / 400 / 500</strong></span>
      </div>
      <div class="type-alpha type-alpha-display">Aa</div>
      <p class="type-sample" style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.4; color: var(--text-1, var(--text));">A modern Garamond. Used for the largest type on every page. Light weights at large sizes feel editorial and confident.</p>
      <p class="type-sample"><em>Italic display renders in <span class="type-accent-em">accent purple</span> — emphasis without weight.</em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div class="type-meta">
        <span>Family<strong>Inter</strong></span>
        <span>Role<strong>Body / UI</strong></span>
        <span>Weights<strong>400 / 500 / 600</strong></span>
      </div>
      <div class="type-alpha type-alpha-body">Aa</div>
      <p class="type-sample">The workhorse. Body copy, UI, subsection headings. Variable weights from 400 (regular body) to 600 (subheadings). Body line-height is generous (1.75) so the page breathes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="type-specimen">
      <div class="type-meta">
        <span>Family<strong>JetBrains Mono</strong></span>
        <span>Role<strong>Metadata / labels</strong></span>
        <span>Weights<strong>300 / 400 / 500</strong></span>
      </div>
      <div class="type-alpha type-alpha-mono">Aa</div>
      <p class="type-sample" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-3); line-height: 1.6;">TAGS · EYEBROW LABELS · METADATA · NUMBERS · STATUS · TIMESTAMPS · ALWAYS UPPERCASED AT SMALL SIZES · +0.12EM TRACKING · NEVER FOR HEADLINES</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <table class="type-scale">
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Class</th><th>Sample</th><th>Spec</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="type-class">Display</span></td>
        <td class="type-scale-sample" style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 36px; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">melis.ai</td>
        <td class="type-scale-spec">Cormorant · 36 · 400 · −0.02em</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="type-class">H1</span></td>
        <td class="type-scale-sample" style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 40px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -0.03em;">Build something that lasts.</td>
        <td class="type-scale-spec">Cormorant · 44 · 300 · −0.03em</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="type-class">H2</span></td>
        <td class="type-scale-sample" style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 26px; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">Section headlines</td>
        <td class="type-scale-spec">Cormorant · 28 · 300 · −0.02em</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="type-class">H3</span></td>
        <td class="type-scale-sample" style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Subsection / chapter</td>
        <td class="type-scale-spec">Inter · 15 · 600 · −0.01em</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="type-class">Body</span></td>
        <td class="type-scale-sample" style="font-size: 13px;">All body copy and paragraphs.</td>
        <td class="type-scale-spec">Inter · 13 · 400 · 1.75</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="type-class">Label</span></td>
        <td class="type-scale-sample" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-3);">Eyebrow · metadata · status</td>
        <td class="type-scale-spec">JetBrains Mono · 10 · +0.12em</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

